Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:37.97,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Clarão!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.38,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Urso Demônio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:49.53,Main,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gavota...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:50.76,Main,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Salte em frente!
